SELECT *
FROM DNACUSTOM.VW_DIGITALBANKING_ACCTBAL
WHERE TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(DATELASTMAINT, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS'), 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') BETWEEN

TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSDATE - INTERVAL '1' HOUR, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS'), 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS')

   AND TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSDATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS'), 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS')

FROM DNACUSTOM.VW_DIGITALBANKING_ACCTLOCKOUT

WHERE TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(DATELASTMAINT, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS'), 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS') BETWEEN

TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSDATE - INTERVAL '1' HOUR, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS'), 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS')

   AND TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSDATE, 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS'), 'YYYY-MM-DD"T"HH24:MI:SS')

    AND (InActiveDate IS NULL OR InActiveDate >= SYSDATE);
